be democratic while providing safeguards against international 
marxism which he said had subjected the country to a constant 
and indiscriminate agression 
the government has said it will not recognize foreigners who 
come to observe the vote a group of excongressmen opposed to 
pinochet has said it expects at least 300 foreigners many of them 
officials in their countries to come as observers 
 
