a front moved in morrison said 
this should be the end of it at least for now harrison 
said in new york 
its a strange phenomenon he added it happens 
occasionally with volcanoes they spew smoke and it gets trapped in 
a particular layer of the atmosphere and it can go all around the 
globe 
