spartan philosophy has helped engender the competition some rivals 
claim to offer more flexibility soft beds instead of sleeping 
bags filet mignon instead of freezedried soup 
one example is atlantabased executive adventure inc founded 
about six years ago by robert carr a 38yearold former head of an 
