mrs madoff 60 says the similarity between their last names 
has benefited both at election time 
she gets elected and i get elected on each others votes 
mrs madoff says every time im not running people say honey 
i voted for you 
as mayor mrs masloff has adopted caliguiris top priorities of 
cutting the citys 4 percent wage tax and advancing pittsburghs 
