sgt lloyd hopkins is the kind of cop who wears his profession 
on his chest in big red letters hes a cop he makes his own rules 
and breaks others and he doesnt care who he has to whack in order 
to rid the world of bad guys and scum 
all this makes sgt lloyd hopkins james woods infinitely more 
dangerous than jack the ripper 
hes a married man who thinks nothing of giving a hooker a 
whirl and a father who tells his small daughter bedtime stories 
about his violent escapades in the understatement of the video 
year his wife tells him hes a very sick man and she takes the 
kid and leaves him 
hopkins doesnt have time to brood about crimes of the heart 
hes hot on the heels of a serial killer 
hopkins is the one man who thinks a serial killer is involved in 
the obscene murder of a young woman hes convinced she is the 15th 
victim of the same murderer and becomes obsessed in the hunt 
charles durning puts in a good performance as hopkins buddy and 
superior and charles haid of tvs hill street blues is fine as 
a sleazy homosexual cop on the take 
but lesley ann warrens feminist poet the killers secret love 
